{"id":911,"parent_id":909,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":911,"title":"Amos 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"Amos","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","The Lord will pour out judgments upon Moab, Judah, and Israel for their unrighteousness."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.1","order":"02.31.002.61122"},["b","1"],"Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; For three transgressions of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Moab"],", and for four, I will not turn away",["i","the punishment"],"thereof; because he burned the bones of the king of Edom into lime:"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.2","order":"02.31.002.61123"},["b","2"],"But I will send a fire upon Moab, and it shall devour the palaces of Kerioth: and Moab shall die with tumult, with shouting,",["i","and"],"with the sound of the trumpet:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.3","order":"02.31.002.61124"},["b","3"],"And I will cut off the judge from the midst thereof, and will slay all the princes thereof with him, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.4","order":"02.31.002.61125"},["b","4"],"¶Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; For three transgressions of Judah, and for four, I will not turn away",["i","the punishment"],"thereof; because they have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"despised"],"the law of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and have not kept his commandments, and their lies caused them to err, after the which their fathers have walked:"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.5","order":"02.31.002.61126"},["b","5"],"But I will send a fire upon Judah, and it shall devour the palaces of Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.6","order":"02.31.002.61127"},["b","6"],"¶Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; For three transgressions of Israel, and for four, I will not turn away",["i","the punishment"],"thereof; because they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"sold"],"the righteous for silver, and the poor for a pair of shoes;"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.7","order":"02.31.002.61128"},["b","7"],"That pant after the dust of the earth on the head of the poor, and turn aside the way of the meek: and a man and his father will go in unto the",["i","same"],"maid, to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"profane"],"my holy name:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.8","order":"02.31.002.61129"},["b","8"],"And they lay",["i","themselves"],"down upon clothes laid to pledge by every altar, and they drink the wine of the condemned",["i","in"],"the house of their god."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.9","order":"02.31.002.61130"},["b","9"],"¶Yet",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"destroyed"],"I the Amorite before them, whose height",["i","was"],"like the height of the cedars, and he",["i","was"],"strong as the oaks; yet I destroyed his fruit from above, and his roots from beneath."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.10","order":"02.31.002.61131"},["b","10"],"Also I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"brought"],"you up from the land of Egypt, and led you",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"forty"],"years through the wilderness, to possess the land of the Amorite."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.11","order":"02.31.002.61132"},["b","11"],"And I raised up of your sons for prophets, and of your young men for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Nazarites"],".",["i","Is it"],"not even thus, O ye children of Israel? saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.12","order":"02.31.002.61133"},["b","12"],"But ye gave the Nazarites wine to drink; and commanded the prophets, saying, Prophesy not."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.13","order":"02.31.002.61134"},["b","13"],"Behold, I am pressed under you, as a cart is pressed",["i","that is"],"full of sheaves."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.14","order":"02.31.002.61135"},["b","14"],"Therefore the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"flight"],"shall perish from the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"swift"],", and the strong shall not strengthen his force, neither shall the mighty",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"deliver"],"himself:"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.15","order":"02.31.002.61136"},["b","15"],"Neither shall he stand that handleth the bow; and",["i","he that is"],"swift of foot shall not deliver",["i","himself:"],"neither shall he that rideth the horse",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"deliver"],"himself."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.16","order":"02.31.002.61137"},["b","16"],"And",["i","he that is"],"courageous among the mighty shall flee away naked in that day, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.1a","order":"02.31.002.61138"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/16.13"},"Isa. 16:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.4a","order":"02.31.002.61140"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/26.14.14-15"},"Lev. 26:14 (14–15)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.6a","order":"02.31.002.61142"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/8.6"},"Amos 8:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.7a","order":"02.31.002.61144"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacrilege"},"TG Sacrilege"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.9a","order":"02.31.002.61146"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/21.24.21-25"},"Num. 21:24 (21–25)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/24.8"},"Josh. 24:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.10a","order":"02.31.002.61148"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/12.51"},"Ex. 12:51"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/3.1"},"Amos 3:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.10b","order":"02.31.002.61150"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/14.33"},"Num. 14:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.11a","order":"02.31.002.61152"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/6.2.2-21"},"Num. 6:2 (2–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.14a","order":"02.31.002.61154"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/9.1"},"Amos 9:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.14b","order":"02.31.002.61156"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.11"},"Eccl. 9:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.14c","order":"02.31.002.61158"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/deliver"},"TG Deliver"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.15a","order":"02.31.002.61160"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/33.17"},"Ps. 33:17"],"."]]}
